OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKen Bruce signs off final  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC Radio 2 show           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, DJ Ken Bruce paid tribute to his       
OL,6, listeners as he signed off from BBC    
OL,7, Radio 2 after more than three decades  
OL,8, of hosting the mid-morning show.       
OL,10,FThe Scottish presenter, 72, is leaving 
OL,11,Fthe network to join commercial station 
OL,12,FGreatest Hits Radio.                   
OL,14,FBruce closed Friday's programme by     
OL,15,Fplaying Golden Slumbers by the Beatles.
OL,17,F"Thank you to everybody who has        
OL,18,Fcontributed in any small way to this   
OL,19,Fprogramme, particularly the listeners,"
OL,20,Fhe said.                               
